timeCreated - Variable in class Order
 
toString() - Method in class Table
 
truncate(Object, Integer) - Static method in class helpers.TextUtil
Truncates the string representation of the input object to the given length.
Truncated strings will end with ..., unless adding it would make the output string longer than lengthLimit.
If lengthLimit is not provided, then the string will be truncated to the length defined at TextUtil.DEFAULT_TRUNC_LENGTH.
The shortest length that strings can be truncated to is controlled by TextUtil.TRUNCATE_MIN_LENGTH.
TRUNCATE_MIN_LENGTH - Static variable in class helpers.TextUtil
The shortest length that strings can be truncated to by TextUtil.truncate(Object, Integer).
